"title": "4195: spirits",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4195",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Intelligent beings which exist separately from bodies. God is spirit and he has given human beings a spiritual entity. He has also created a realm of spiritual beings--some have remained good, others have become evil. Evil spirits seek to control and destroy people, but Jesus Christ has the victory over them.</p>\n<h2>God is spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:24\">JHN 4:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">GEN 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:4\">JOB 33:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:4\">REV 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:1\">REV 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:5\">REV 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:6\">REV 5:6</a></p>\n<h2>Other spirits</h2>\n<h3>The spirit of human beings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:27\">PRO 20:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:8\">JOB 32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:7\">ECC 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:55\">LUK 8:55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:46\">LUK 23:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:6\">JHN 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:59\">ACT 7:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:26\">JAS 2:26</a></p>\n<h3>The spirits of the dead</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:14\">ISA 26:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:18\">PRO 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:9\">ISA 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:23\">HEB 12:23</a></p>\n<h3>Angels</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:14\">HEB 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:21-Judg6:22\">JDG 6:21–6:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:20-Judg13:21\">JDG 13:20–13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:5\">ZEC 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:8\">ACT 23:8</a></p>\n<h3>Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:6\">JOB 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:1\">JOB 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:14\">2CO 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11-Eph6:12\">EPH 6:11–6:12</a></p>\n<h3>Demons</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:13-Rev16:14\">REV 16:13–16:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:18\">LUK 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:21\">LUK 7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:8\">ACT 23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:19\">1PE 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:2\">REV 18:2</a></p>\n<h2>The role of spirits</h2>\n<h3>As instruments of punishment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:14\">1SA 16:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:23\">JDG 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:10\">1SA 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:9\">1SA 19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:20-1Kgs22:22\">1KI 22:20–22:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:19-2Chr18:21\">2CH 18:19–18:21</a></p>\n<h3>As instruments of testing to inspire faith in believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8-1Pet5:9\">1PE 5:8–5:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:8-Job1:12\">JOB 1:8–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:22\">JOB 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:3-Job2:6\">JOB 2:3–2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:10\">JOB 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1\">MAT 4:1</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:13\">MRK 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:2\">LUK 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7-Jas4:8\">JAS 4:7–4:8</a></p>\n<h2>Evil spirits and humanity</h2>\n<h3>Possession by spirits</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:17-Mark9:18\">MRK 9:17–9:18</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:39\">LUK 9:39</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:28\">MAT 8:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:27\">LUK 8:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:22\">MAT 15:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:25\">MRK 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:23\">MRK 1:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:33\">LUK 4:33</a></p>\n<h3>Casting out spirits</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:16\">MAT 8:16</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:34\">MRK 1:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:40\">LUK 4:40</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28\">MAT 12:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:20\">LUK 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:18\">MAT 17:18</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:25-Mark9:26\">MRK 9:25–9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:42\">LUK 9:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:16\">ACT 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:7\">ACT 8:7</a></p>\n<h3>Consultation with spirits forbidden</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:10-Deut18:11\">DEU 18:10–18:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:31\">LEV 19:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:6\">LEV 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:8-1Sam28:9\">1SA 28:8–28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:6\">2KI 21:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:6\">2CH 33:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:19\">ISA 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:3\">ISA 19:3</a></p>\n<h2>Discernment and testing of spirits</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1\">1JN 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:10\">1CO 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:2-1John4:6\">1JN 4:2–4:6</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ has supremacy over all created spirits</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:10\">COL 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:24-Mark1:27\">MRK 1:24–1:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:34\">MRK 1:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:41\">LUK 4:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:33-Luke4:36\">LUK 4:33–4:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:17-Luke10:19\">LUK 10:17–10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:15\">COL 2:15</a></p>",
